msgid "‘uppannaṃ kho me idaṃ upekkhindriyaṃ, tañca kho sanimittaṃ sanidānaṃ sasaṅkhāraṃ sappaccayaṃ. "
msgstr "‘The faculty of equanimity has arisen in me. And that has a foundation, a source, a condition, and a reason. "

