msgctxt "sn48.40:5.6"
msgid "Kattha cuppannaṃ upekkhindriyaṃ aparisesaṃ nirujjhati? "
msgstr "And where does that faculty of equanimity that’s arisen cease without anything left over? "

msgctxt "sn48.40:5.7"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sabbaso nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṃ samatikkamma saññāvedayitanirodhaṃ upasampajja viharati, "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant, going totally beyond the dimension of neither perception nor non-perception, enters and remains in the cessation of perception and feeling. "

msgctxt "sn48.40:5.8"
msgid "ettha cuppannaṃ upekkhindriyaṃ aparisesaṃ nirujjhati. "
msgstr "That’s where the faculty of equanimity that’s arisen ceases without anything left over. "

msgctxt "sn48.40:5.9"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, ‘bhikkhu aññāsi upekkhindriyassa nirodhaṃ, tadatthāya cittaṃ upasaṃharatī’”ti. "
msgstr "They’re called a mendicant who understands the cessation of the faculty of equanimity, and who applies their mind to that end.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn48.40:5.10"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn48.40:5.11"
msgid "Sukhindriyavaggo catuttho. "
msgstr " "

